s transform employee engagement and retention by creating structured and inspiring career pathways.<\/span><\/p><h3><b>This session will:<\/b><\/h3><ol><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Provide Clarity<\/b><b><br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Discover how clear career paths eliminate uncertainty and show employees exactly where their hard work can lead, boosting morale and productivity.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Showcase Options<\/b><b><br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Explore how offering multiple career pathways\u2014technical, leadership, project management, and more\u2014empowers your employees with flexibility and choice, building loyalty and long-term commitment.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Demonstrate Support<\/b><b><br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Learn how to align learning and development initiatives with career paths to show employees you\u2019re invested in their growth and success.<\/span><\/li><\/ol>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"section"},{"id":"4a0b86bb","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Your Presenter<\/b><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"538d710f","settings":{"editor":"<h2 class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM | Engineering Management Institute<\/b><\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"41838a4","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-55130 size-medium\" title=\"Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"EMI- Your Engineering Career\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most AEC organizations are too busy to focus on attracting, developing, and retaining talented professionals, making it hard to grow. Through his work a tEMI, Fasano utilizes a proven framework to help organizations, both public and private, build professional development plans, programs, and tools that help them attract, build, AND maintain strong teams and grow sustainably.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fasano has written a bestselling book entitled <\/span><b><i>Engineer Your Own Success <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(by IEEE-Wiley Press)<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and under his stewardship, EMI has built a massive content platform including 10 active podcasts, 3 YouTube channels, and a popular blog dedicated to helping AEC professionals become better managers and leaders.<\/span><\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"50","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_posi